  "body": "`Version      : 1.8.26-0-8c43ca573-20200427/X64-Microsoft Windows 10.0.18363/Core3.1.1`\r\n\r\nIn my config file I have this:\r\n`\"LogFileName\": \"C:/Nethermind/MyData/Log/Mainnet.log\"`\r\n\r\nYour default mainnet.cfg file has this:\r\n`\"LogFileName\": \"mainnet.logs.txt\"`\r\n\r\nBut in reality it's logging to:\r\n`<exe_path>\\logs\\log.txt`\r\n\r\nThis was working prior to `1.8.26`",
